title: El Diablo
description:
Issues 1-4 of 'El Diablo'

Vertigo/DC Comics, 2001, 24 pages each

Written by Brian Azzerello

Illustrated by Danijel Zezelj

Small-town sheriff Moses Stone is running from his past, and from something even worse: the legendary El Diablo, a relentless, violent gunman who has unearthed the skeletons in Stone's closet. Is El Diablo a man on a mission, or is he a spirit of atonement avenging the ghosts of the past?
